'''Intention as Psi Source''' is the framework hypothesis that '''focused conscious attention''' is the primary mechanism by which the [[Psi Field]] is sourced and modulated by a human operator. In the quantum picture, an intentional source <math>J_\psi</math> is a coherent driver of [[Psion|psion]] production: it pumps psions into low-momentum modes whose coherent-state superposition is the classical ψ-field configuration the operator experiences as "charging up" or "pressure". This page is the conceptual bridge between subjective will and the framework's field-theoretic formalism.

